#. Type: text
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:1001
msgid "Software RAID device"
msgstr "Dyfais RAID meddalwedd"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:2001
msgid "Configure software RAID"
msgstr "Cyflunio RAID meddalwedd"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#. What is "in use" is a partition
#: ../partman-md.templates:3001
msgid "In use by software RAID device ${DEVICE}"
msgstr "Mewn defnydd gan ddyfais RAID meddalwedd ${DEVICE}"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:4001
msgid "Software RAID not available"
msgstr "RAID meddalwedd ddim ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:4001
msgid ""
"The current kernel doesn't seem to support software RAID (MD) devices. This "
"should be solved by loading the necessary modules."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw'r cnewyllyn cyfredol yn cynnal dyfeisiau RAID meddalwedd (MD). Dylid "
"datrys hyn drwy lwytho'r modiwlau angenrheidiol."

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#. Note to translators : Please keep your translations of the choices
#. below a 65 columns limit (which means 65 characters
#. in single-byte languages)
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:5001
msgid "Create MD device"
msgstr "Creu dyfais Amlddisg (MD)"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#. Note to translators : Please keep your translations of the choices
#. below a 65 columns limit (which means 65 characters
#. in single-byte languages)
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:5001
msgid "Delete MD device"
msgstr "Dileu dyfais Amlddisg (MD)"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#. Note to translators : Please keep your translations of the choices
#. below a 65 columns limit (which means 65 characters
#. in single-byte languages)
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:5001
msgid "Finish"
msgstr "Gorffen"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:5002
msgid "Software RAID configuration actions"
msgstr "Gweithredoedd cyflunio RAID meddalwedd"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:5002
msgid ""
"This is the software RAID (or MD, \"multiple device\") configuration menu."
msgstr "Dyma ddewislen RAID meddalwedd (MD, neu \"aml ddyfais\")."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:5002
msgid "Please select one of the proposed actions to configure software RAID."
msgstr ""
"Dewiswch un o'r gweithredoedd a gynigir er mwyn cyflunio RAID meddalwedd."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:6001
msgid "Software RAID device type:"
msgstr "Math dyfais RAID meddalwedd:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:6001
msgid "Please choose the type of the software RAID device to be created."
msgstr "Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiswch y math o RAID meddalwedd i'w greu."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:7001
msgid "No RAID partitions available"
msgstr "Dim rhaniadau RAID ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:7001
msgid ""
"No unused partitions of the type \"Linux RAID Autodetect\" are available. "
"Please create such a partition, or delete an already used software RAID "
"device to free its partitions."
msgstr ""
"Nid oes rhaniadau heb ei ddefnyddio o'r math \"RAID Linux Awtoddarganfod\" "
"ar gael. Crëwch rhaniad o'r math yma os gwelwch yn dda, neu dilewch ddyfais "
"RAID meddalwedd a ddefnyddir eisioes er mwyn rhyddhau ei raniadau."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:7001
msgid ""
"If you have such partitions, they might contain actual file systems, and are "
"therefore not available for use by this configuration utility."
msgstr ""
"Os oes y fath rhaniadau gennych, fe allent gynnwys systemau ffeiliau, a "
"felly nid ydynt ar gael i'w defnyddio gan y teclyn cyflunio hwn."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:8001
msgid "Active devices for the RAID0 array:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer yr araë RAID0:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:8001
msgid ""
"You have chosen to create a RAID0 array. Please choose the active devices in "
"this array."
msgstr ""
"Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID0. Dewiswch y dyfeisiau gweithredol yn yr "
"araë hwn."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:9001
msgid "Number of active devices for the RAID${LEVEL} array:"
msgstr "Nifer y dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer yr araë RAID${LEVEL}:"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:9001
msgid ""
"The RAID${LEVEL} array will consist of both active and spare devices. The "
"active devices are those used, while the spare devices will only be used if "
"one or more of the active devices fail. A minimum of ${MINIMUM} active "
"devices is required."
msgstr ""
"Fe fydd yr araë RAID${LEVEL} yn cynnwys rhaniadau gweithredol a sbâr. "
"Defnyddir y rhaniadau gweithredol, tra caiff y dyfeisiau sbâr eu defnyddio "
"dim ond os yw un neu fwy o'r dyfeisiau gweithredol yn methu. Mae'n rhaid "
"cael lleiafrif o ${MINIMUM} dyfais."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:9001 ../partman-md.templates:14001
msgid "NOTE: this setting cannot be changed later."
msgstr "SYLWER: ni ellir newid y gosodiad yma wedyn."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:10001
msgid "Active devices for the RAID${LEVEL} array:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer yr araë RAID${LEVEL}:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:10001
msgid ""
"You have chosen to create a RAID${LEVEL} array with ${COUNT} active devices."
msgstr ""
"Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID${LEVEL} gyda ${COUNT} dyfais gweithredol."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:10001
msgid ""
"Please choose which partitions are active devices. You must select exactly "
"${COUNT} partitions."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiswch pa rhaniadau sy'n ddyfeisiau gweithredol. Rhaid "
"i chi ddewis ${COUNT} rhaniad yn union."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:11001
msgid "Number of spare devices for the RAID${LEVEL} array:"
msgstr "Nifer o ddyfeisiau sbâr ar gyfer yr araë RAID${LEVEL}:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:12001
msgid "Spare devices for the RAID${LEVEL} array:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau sbâr ar gyfer yr araë RAID${LEVEL}:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:12001
msgid ""
"You have chosen to create a RAID${LEVEL} array with ${COUNT} spare devices."
msgstr "Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID${LEVEL} gyda ${COUNT} dyfais sbâr."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:12001
msgid ""
"Please choose which partitions will be used as spare devices. You may choose "
"up to ${COUNT} partitions. If you choose less than ${COUNT} devices, the "
"remaining partitions will be added to the array as \"missing\". You will be "
"able to add them to the array later."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiswch pa rhaniadau a caiff eu defnyddio fel dyfeisiau "
"sbâr. Cewch ddewis hyd at ${COUNT} rhaniad. Os ydych chi'n dewis llai na "
"${COUNT} dyfais, caiff y rhaniadau dros ben eu ychwanegu fel \"ar goll\". "
"Cewch eu hychwanegu nhw i'r araë nes ymlaen."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:13001
msgid "Not enough RAID partitions available"
msgstr "Dim digon o raniadau RAID ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:13001
msgid ""
"There are not enough RAID partitions available for your selected "
"configuration.  You have ${NUM_PART} RAID partitions available but your "
"configuration requires ${REQUIRED} partitions."
msgstr ""
"Does dim digon o raniadau RAID ar gael ar gyfer eich cyfluniad dewisiesig. "
"Mae gennych ${NUM_PART} rhaniad RAID ar gael ond mae eich cyfluniad yn mynnu "
"${REQUIRED} rhaniad."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:14001
msgid "Layout of the RAID10 array:"
msgstr "Cynllun yr arae RAID10:"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:14001
msgid ""
"The layout must be n, o, or f (arrangement of the copies) followed by a "
"number (number of copies of each chunk). The number must be smaller or equal "
"to the number of active devices."
msgstr ""
"Rhaid i'r cynllun fod yn n, o neu f (trefniant y copïau) wedi ei ddilyn gan "
"rif (nifer o gopïau o bob talp). Rhaid i'r rhif fod yn llai neu hafal i'r "
"nifer o ddyfeisiau gweithredol."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:14001
msgid ""
"The letter is the arrangement of the copies:\n"
" n - near copies: Multiple copies of one data block are at similar\n"
"     offsets in different devices.\n"
" f - far copies: Multiple copies have very different offsets\n"
" o - offset copies: Rather than the chunks being duplicated within a\n"
"     stripe, whole stripes are duplicated but are rotated by one\n"
"     device so duplicate blocks are on different devices."
msgstr ""
"Y llythyren yw'r trefniant o gopïau:\n"
"n - copïau agos (near): Mae amryw gopïau o'r un bloc data ar\n"
"     atredau tebyg ar ddyfeisiau gwahanol.\n"
"f - copïau pell (far): Mae amryw gopïau ar atredau gwahanol iawn\n"
"o - copïau atred (offset): Yn hytrach na talpiau yn cael eu dyblygu o\n"
"     fewn streip, mae streipiau cyfan yn cael eu dyblygu ond yn cael\n"
"     eu cylchdroi o un dyfais felly fe fydd blociau dyblyg ar wahanol\n"
"     ddyfeisiau."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:15001
msgid "Software RAID device to be deleted:"
msgstr "Dyfais RAID meddalwedd i'w ddileu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:15001
msgid ""
"Deleting a software RAID device will stop it and clear the superblock of all "
"its components."
msgstr ""
"Mi fydd dileu dyfais RAID meddalwedd yn ei stopio ac yna clirio'r uwchfloc "
"o'i holl gydrannau."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:15001
msgid ""
"Please note this will not immediately allow you to reuse the partitions or "
"devices in a new software RAID device. The array will however be unusable "
"after the deletion."
msgstr ""
"Sylwer na fydd hyn yn caniatáu i chi ailddefnyddio'r rhaniadau na dyfeisiau "
"mewn dyfais RAID meddalwedd newydd yn syth. Fodd bynnag, ni ellir "
"defnyddio'r araë ar ol y dilëad."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:15001
msgid ""
"If you select a device for deletion, you will get some information about it "
"and you will be given the option of aborting this operation."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n dewis dileu dyfais, cewch fanylion amdano a cyfle i beidio "
"mynd ymlaen â'r weithred."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:16001
msgid "No software RAID devices available"
msgstr "Nid oes dyfeisiau RAID meddalwedd ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:16001
msgid "No software RAID devices are available for deletion."
msgstr "Nid oes dyfeisiau RAID meddalwedd ar gael i'w dileu."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:17001
msgid "Really delete this software RAID device?"
msgstr "Gwir ddileu'r ddyfais RAID meddalwedd hwn?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:17001
msgid ""
"Please confirm whether you really want to delete the following software RAID "
"device:"
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, cadarnhewch eich bod am ddileu y ddyfais RAID meddalwedd "
"canlynol:"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:17001
msgid ""
" Device:            ${DEVICE}\n"
" Type:              ${TYPE}\n"
" Component devices:"
msgstr ""
" Dyfais:            ${DEVICE}\n"
" Math:              ${TYPE}\n"
" Dyfeisiau cydran:"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:18001
msgid "Failed to delete the software RAID device"
msgstr "Methwyd dileu y ddyfais RAID meddalwedd"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:18001
msgid "There was an error deleting the software RAID device. It may be in use."
msgstr ""
"Roedd gwall wrth ddileu y ddyfais RAID meddalwedd. Efallai ei fod mewn "
"defnydd."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:19001
msgid "Write the changes to the storage devices and configure RAID?"
msgstr "Ysgrifennu'r newidiadau i'r dyfeisiau storfa a chyflunio RAID?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:19001
msgid ""
"Before RAID can be configured, the changes have to be written to the storage "
"devices.  These changes cannot be undone."
msgstr ""
"Cyn gellir cyflunio RAID, rhaid ysgrifennu'r newidiadau i'r dyfeisiau "
"storfa. Ni ellir dadwneud y newidiadau yma."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:19001 ../partman-md.templates:20001
msgid ""
"When RAID is configured, no additional changes to the partitions in the "
"disks containing physical volumes are allowed.  Please convince yourself "
"that you are satisfied with the current partitioning scheme in these disks."
msgstr ""
"Pan mae RAID wedi ei gyflunio, ni chaniateir unrhyw newidiadau i'r rhaniadau "
"yn y disgiau sy'n cynnwys cyfrolau corfforol. Os gwelwch yn dda, sicrhewch "
"eich bod chi'n fodlon gyda'r cynllun rhaniadu cyfredol yn y disgiau hyn."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:20001
msgid "Keep current partition layout and configure RAID?"
msgstr "Cadw'r cynllun rhaniad cyfredol a chyflunio RAID?"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:21001
msgid "RAID configuration failure"
msgstr "Methiant cyfluniad RAID"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:21001
msgid "An error occurred while writing the changes to the storage devices."
msgstr "Digwyddodd gwall wrth ysgrifennu'r newidiadau i'r dyfeisiau storfa."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:21001
msgid "RAID configuration has been aborted."
msgstr "Mae cyflunio RAID wedi ei derfynu."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:22001
msgid "physical volume for RAID"
msgstr "cyfrol corfforol ar gyfer RAID"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:23001
msgid "raid"
msgstr "raid"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:24001
msgid "Remove existing software RAID partitions?"
msgstr "Dileu y rhaniadau RAID meddalwedd presennol?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:24001
msgid ""
"The selected device contains partitions used for software RAID devices. The "
"following devices and partitions are about to be removed:"
msgstr ""
"Mae'r ddyfais ddewiswyd yn cynnwys rhaniadau ar gyfer dyfeisiau RAID "
"meddalwedd. Mae'r dyfeisiau a'r rhaniadau canlynol am gael eu dileu:"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:24001
msgid "Software RAID devices about to be removed: ${REMOVED_DEVICES}"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau RAID meddalwedd ar fin cael eu dileu: ${REMOVED_DEVICES}"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:24001
msgid "Partitions used by these RAID devices: ${REMOVED_PARTITIONS}"
msgstr ""
"Y rhaniadau sy'n cael eu defnyddio gan y dyfeisiau RAID hyn: "
"${REMOVED_PARTITIONS}"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#. :sl3:
#: ../partman-md.templates:24001
msgid ""
"Note that this will also permanently erase any data currently on the "
"software RAID devices."
msgstr ""
"Noder y bydd hwn yn dileu yn barhaol unrhyw ddata sy'n bresennol ar y "
"dyfeisiau RAID meddalwedd."
